<Layout title="DC Pastel">
  <main class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden">
    <video
      autoplay
      loop
      muted
      playsinline
      class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0"
    >
      <track
        src="captions_en.vtt"
        kind="captions"
        srclang="en"
        label="english_captions"
      />
      <track
        src="captions_es.vtt"
        kind="captions"
        srclang="es"
        label="spanish_captions"
      />
      <source src="video-dc-pastel.webm" type="video/mp4" />
      Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>

    <div
      class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-2 md:px-6 py-4 md:py-20 flex items-center"
    >
      <section
        class="w-full bg-white bg-opacity-40 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-8 md:p-12 md:px-4 backdrop-blur-sm"
      >
        <div class="mx-auto text-center">
          <h1
            class="text-pink-600 font-bold text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-6 animate-fade-in"
          >
            Bienvenidos a DC Pastel
          </h1>
          <div class="w-full md:w-3/4 mx-auto">
            <p
              class="text-gray-700 text-lg md:text-xl mb-8 leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-delay"
            >
              Donde cada tarta es una explosión de sabor y creatividad,
              transformando momentos simples en celebraciones inolvidables.
              Descubre la magia en cada bocado. ¡Sumérgete en el dulce mundo de
              DC Pastel hoy mismo!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-8 animate-fade-in-delay-2"
          >
            <a
              href="#"
              class="bg-pink-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:bg-pink-600 hover:shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              Conóceme
            </a>
            <a
              href="#"
              class="bg-white text-pink-700 border-2 border-pink-500 px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:bg-pink-100 hover:shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              Galería
            </a>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-8 sm:gap-24 animate-fade-in-delay-2"
          >
            <a
              href="#"
              class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              <Instagram />
              <span class="">Instagram</span>
            </a>
            <a
              href="#"
              class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              <Facebook />
              <span class="">Facebook</span>
            </a>
            <a
              href="#"
              class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              <Whatsapp />
              <span class="">Whatsapp</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <style>
      @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      .animate-fade-in {
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
      }

      .animate-fade-in-delay {
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out 0.3s forwards;
        opacity: 0;
      }

      .animate-fade-in-delay-2 {
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out 0.6s forwards;
        opacity: 0;
      }
    </style>
  </main></Layout
